data.description: Amazing opportunity in the RV friendly neighborhood of Savannah, in growing Litchfield Park! This 3634 sq ft open floor plan gorgeous home is on an over sized 11.700 sq ft lot. w/split 3 car garage & oversize RV garage (22' X 50') w/front & rear doors & 220 Amp-room for all your toys! Plus 1 year old spa. Meticulously maintained by the original owner, this home offers luxurious space inside w/ 5 bedrooms & 2.5 baths. Gourmet kitchen features upgraded cabinetry w/crown molding, granite, pull out shelves & spice rack, double ovens, gas stove-all SS appliances. 2 pantries, one walk & Butler's pantry. Bedroom & half bath downstairs as well as formal dining. Huge loft upstairs that could be a game room or den/office.  All upstairs bedrooms have walk-in closets & the primary suite features separate shower & tub, double sinks and a large walk in closet with a window. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity!
